energy grid the secondary energy-angle distributions are          2049 1451
specified by means of the relative emission spectra and the       2049 1451
parameters for the Kalbach systematics for angular distributions. 2049 1451
Next, the photon yield is tabulated as a function of incident     2049 1451
energy. For each incident energy, the photon production is given  2049 1451
